Name: Smithing Materials Farming
Description:
Buy Elden Ring Smithing Materials to get a chance to upgrade all your Gear up to the maximum! All Smithing materials, such as Smithing Stones, Somber Smithing Stones, Grave Glovewort, and Ghost Glovewort, are scattered around The Lands Between. Collecting enough to upgrade all desired weapons and inventory can be very long and tedious. However, Skycoach can fix that! With our Elden Ring Materials farm, you can upgrade your Gear as much as you want effortlessly!
You will get:
Chosen amount of desired Material packs (each pack contains 10 Materials);
Any Material Tier that you choose, up to the highest: Ancient Dragon Smithing Stones, Somber Ancient Dragon Smithing Stones, Great Grave Glovewort, and Great Ghost Glovewort.
A possibility of maximizing your Gear's stats.
Prepare to beat Elden Ring's main game and DLC much easier!

Name: Flask Upgrades
Description:
Buy Elden Ring Flask Upgrades to maximize the amount of healing and FP restoration effortlessly. Both Sacred Tears and Golden Seeds are hard-to-find Materials scattered around the entire huge open-world map. Golden Seeds increase the amount of Flasks available, while Sacred Tears increase their effectiveness. You can get them all without struggling with our Sacred Tears and Golden Seeds service.
You will obtain:
The chosen amount of Sacred Tears or Golden Seeds;
A possibility to maximally upgrade your Crimson and Cerulean Flasks.
Prepare to beat Elden Ring's main game and DLC much easier!
